<p>In Sweden the Ume&#229; Plant Science Center (UPSC) has 
been created by moving plant groups from the Ume&#229; 
University and Swedis University of Agricultural Sciences 
(Ume&#229;) to the same building. Groups there have also 
received a national center of excellence status and funding 
