concentrated in trees (hybrid poplar), but <I>Arabidopsis</I> 
functional genomics is heavily utilized for the determination 
of the function of poplar genes that have a well-conserved 
counterpart in <I>Arabidopsis</I>. The UPSC is also partner 
in the European CATMA-project. Groups in Uppsala University 
are involved in two EU-projects that aim in the elucidation 
of several transcription factors groups in 
<I>Arabidopsis</I>.
